# Revision1 - Spring Boot Application

## Overview
This is a **Spring Boot** application for managing properties, bookings, user authentication, and reviews. It includes JWT-based authentication, AWS S3 integration for image uploads, and Twilio for SMS & WhatsApp notifications.


## Features
- **User Authentication** (JWT-based)
- **Property Management** (CRUD operations)
- **Room Availability & Booking System**
- **Image Uploads (AWS S3)**
- **Review System**
- **Twilio SMS & WhatsApp Notifications**



## Technologies Used
- Spring Boot (Backend framework)
- Spring Security & JWT (Authentication)
- Spring Data JPA (Database interactions)
- Maven (Build tool)
- MySQL/PostgreSQL (Database)
- AWS S3 (Image storage)
- Twilio (SMS & WhatsApp notifications)
- Lombok (For reducing boilerplate code)



